; Regression test for GitHub issue #1009
; ledger crashed with "Exception during initialization:
; boost::filesystem::current_path: No such file or directory"
; when run from a non-existent (deleted) directory.
;
; The fix added safe_current_path() which catches the error_code from
; boost::filesystem::current_path() and falls back to "/" when the
; current working directory is unavailable.
;
; NOTE: The crash scenario (deleted CWD) cannot be reproduced by the
; test harness.  This test serves as a basic smoke test to verify
; ledger runs correctly after the safe_current_path() refactoring.

2024/01/01 Opening Balance
    Assets:Checking         $1000.00
    Equity:Opening

test bal Assets
            $1000.00  Assets:Checking
end test
